                "img": "https://arxiv.org/html/2603.17375/2603.17375v1/x2.png",
                "caption": "Figure 2:World Model Comparison. StereoWorld incorporates metric-scale geometry, producing output modalities that are more compatible with pretrained models. Moreover, it can be applied end-to-end for VR visualization, ensuring better consistency of fine-grained details between the left and right views.",
